## Conclusion

The `fallback.py` implementation has a **critical architectural mismatch** with telegram-claude-bridge. The `/send` and `/health` endpoints work correctly, but the `/register_surface` method calls a non-existent endpoint and will always fail.

**Priority:** HIGH
**Risk:** HIGH - `register_surface()` calls will fail with HTTP 404
**Fix Required:** YES - Remove or stub the non-functional method
